# {{APP_CLI}}

CLI for the {{APP_NAME}} API. Built with [api2cli](https://github.com/Melvynx/api2cli).

## Install

```bash
bun --version || curl -fsSL https://bun.sh/install | bash
npx api2cli create {{APP_NAME}} --base-url {{BASE_URL}} --auth-type {{AUTH_TYPE}}
npx api2cli bundle {{APP_NAME}}
npx api2cli link {{APP_NAME}}
export PATH="$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH"
```

## Install AgentSkill

```bash
npx skills-cli add {{GITHUB_REPO}}
```

Or manually copy `skills/{{APP_CLI}}/SKILL.md` to `~/.claude/skills/{{APP_CLI}}/SKILL.md`.

## Usage

```bash
{{APP_CLI}} auth set "your-token"
{{APP_CLI}} auth test
{{APP_CLI}} --help
```

